To know a class of a program : xprop
To change default browser : edit the browser entry in /home/$USER/.profile then find and replace all Pale Moon entries in /home/$USER/.config/mimeapps.list It usually works with chrome
To disable mouse acceleration : /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/50-mouse-acceleration.conf
Section "InputClass"
	Identifier "My Mouse"
	MatchIsPointer "yes"
	Option "AccelerationProfile" "-1"
	Option "AccelerationScheme" "none"
	Option "AccelSpeed" "-1"
EndSection


